title: The Man from the Pru (1990) Pryce Massey York
description:
The Qualtrough case was notorious in the 1930's - an unsolved murder, mysterious voices on the telephone, a non-existent address. This movie portrays a humble insurance clerk (Jonathan Pryce) getting caught up in matters way over his head.

The music of Charles Guard is a big plus, likewise the shots of foggy streets and alleyways. The opening credits alone are worth the Pryce of admission.
